{"tid":1565914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 有關跳閘建議?]  求指教","createTime":"2019-09-13T10:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T19:29:39.000Z","uid":149790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d4dadd1a1d43e4f9f2fe0ae1e21820e5a8cd6d6c","tid":1565914,"uid":149790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"[忽發奇想] 如果大家即使係俾錢搭黨鐵，但都跳閘，唔好正常地入閘。咁樣就可以分散黨鐵職員 /food panda 嘅注意力。從而令到真係跳閘( 唔俾錢搭車)嘅手足被捉到嘅機會減低。<br />\n因爲都會有唔少人想抵制黨鐵 , 但始終淆底驚俾人捉 。<br />\n我諗正常嘟卡入閘，但只係唔用正常嘅方法入閘，應該冇犯任何規例。所以就算有職員捉到之後，check 返係有俾錢搭車應該吹你唔漲( 有冇熟黨鐵規則嘅爸絲可以講下有冇錯，如有錯歡迎指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"3dbd87562eaafe8fd46e1487a339009dd7dbb534","tid":1565914,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月15日見！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Trzyi1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrzyi1f.jpg&h=f89f6e65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e344c05d009f4e6eb73a55365350c17869848b99","tid":1565914,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:37:14.000Z","msg":"呢排嚴 <br />\n1.單程票入閘 跳出閘<br />\n2.長者卡<br />\n3.跟尾入閘"},{"pid":"7c9f75928d5cc661e7d43f30177fae042617a2de","tid":1565914,"uid":255581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"捐閘好低調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以試下"},{"pid":"9371f6fb20b423dcc2c61e195b366f96b91505ef","tid":1565914,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:16:18.000Z","msg":"【致所有搭黨鐵又唔敢跳閘嘅手足】不如你哋都買返張長者八達通卡啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565989\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565989</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9bf69726b01b2096